1. Behavioural Design Pattern
2. If there is some common steps between 2 or more flows which needs to be followed
    in certain sequence
3. The actual impl will be different
4. You can have some template which can have common flow where clients can override

Payment App -

1. Payment to Friend

2. Payment to Merchant


Common Steps -
============

validateRequest
checkBalance
debit money
charge platform fees - 0 for frnd, 2% for merchant
credit money